# Personal notes with financial/social details — local-only, not for the public repo
notes/OPEN_SOURCE_DECISION.md

# One-off scratch/repair scripts left in the working tree (mostly on the M1).
# Ignoring them matters beyond tidiness: an UNTRACKED file colliding with a
# future tracked filename makes `git pull --ff-only` abort and kills every
# nightly run; git overwrites IGNORED files without complaint.
/_*.py
/retag_*
/repair_*
/validate_full.py
